data.text: @markjgiga @LMKtweets @alicialewisKARE @kare11 The photometrics are impressive. 380 lux at 3m and 90CRI assuming these are 5600 kelvin. Same output as 1k tungsten but only draws 150w. Do you know if these units were DMX enabled?
